                            <p class="mb-3 mb-xl-4">Our programs are tailored to meet your academic goals, fostering growth, innovation, and career advancement. Whether you're seeking to boost your career or explore new passions, our courses provide the perfect pathway. Get in touch with us today and start your journey toward success.</p>
                            <a href="https://www.universityofcebu.net/" class="btn bsb-btn-2xl btn-primary rounded-pill" target="_blank">More Details</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
